data.description: Lovely home in a great location east of 95, close to beaches, shopping and parks. Updated kitchen, 3 bedroom/2 bathroom, high vaulted ceilings, split floor plan, walk in closets, huge fenced in backyard and no HOA. Elementary school down the street. Wont last long!
